00:24:36,980 --> 00:24:39,070
Isn't this good?

247
00:24:47,370 --> 00:24:49,220
Not good.

248
00:24:49,820 --> 00:24:52,140
Is it not good to be with me?

249
00:24:57,700 --> 00:24:59,620
It's very good.

250
00:25:31,450 --> 00:25:35,740
Miss Feng, I never meant to hurt you.

251
00:25:36,250 --> 00:25:38,610
It's your bad luck.

252
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:43,400
Since you and your father have already paid with your lives,

253
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:47,000
I must find Master Shi.

254
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:03,760
With the bloody incident of the auction,

255
00:26:03,760 --> 00:26:07,190
this old fool is not only still at large,

256
00:26:07,190 --> 00:26:10,630
but now he's spreading rumors about me.

257
00:26:10,630 --> 00:26:12,440
Should I kill him?

258
00:26:13,700 --> 00:26:15,060
No, I want to keep an eye on him.

259
00:26:15,060 --> 00:26:19,880
I want to see who on earth is behind this old fool?

260
00:26:19,880 --> 00:26:24,050
Perhaps, we may be able to track down the Longevity Fruit's whereabouts.

261
00:26:24,050 --> 00:26:25,670
Yes.

262
00:26:27,950 --> 00:26:30,490
The old man's corpse inside the hidden chamber that day,

263
00:26:30,490 --> 00:26:32,810
have you found out his identity?

264
00:26:36,740 --> 00:26:39,950
My hidden chamber has lost one vial of a drug.

265
00:26:39,950 --> 00:26:42,530
It's very strange.

266
00:26:42,530 --> 00:26:45,200
Who took it?

267
00:26:48,610 --> 00:26:51,660
Who would dare steal your drugs?

268
00:26:52,610 --> 00:26:54,260
That's also true.

269
00:26:54,260 --> 00:26:58,730
Who is so bold as to steal a vial of 'Three Day Drunk'?

270
00:27:05,530 --> 00:27:08,640
However, that bottle didn't have 'Three Day Drunk' in it.

271
00:27:09,720 --> 00:27:12,640
I switched it with an aphrodisiac.

272
00:27:16,950 --> 00:27:20,140
An aphrodisiac?

273
00:27:20,140 --> 00:27:23,890
Yes. Well, I've never used that drug before,

274
00:27:23,890 --> 00:27:25,940
but they say

275
00:27:25,940 --> 00:27:28,460
that drug was prepared by the Devil.

276
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:47,920
Brother, I have a matter to tend to, I must be going.

277
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:53,580
I have to go.

278
00:28:00,690 --> 00:28:03,740
Xiao Chun Hua poisons me and wants to leave?

279
00:28:12,320 --> 00:28:14,390
I trust you

280
00:28:15,340 --> 00:28:18,200
but you're always lying to me.

281
00:28:22,070 --> 00:28:24,900
So, is that poison that can kill me?

282
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:29,600
No.

283
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:33,110
- Then what is it? 
 - It's an aphrodisiac.

284
00:28:35,320 --> 00:28:37,580
An aphrodisiac?

285
00:28:38,420 --> 00:28:40,730
What's that?

286
00:28:41,850 --> 00:28:46,350
It's just something that arouses you.

287
00:28:47,120 --> 00:28:50,390
Is it a drug that will make you like me more?

288
00:28:55,930 --> 00:28:58,440
Xiao Chun Hua, you are tender-hearted.

289
00:28:58,440 --> 00:29:01,330
You only grabbed the 'Three-Day Drunk.'

290
00:29:01,330 --> 00:29:03,860
You hit the mark by a fluke. 
 (similar to seemingly missing the target but in the end, still hit the target)

291
00:29:03,860 --> 00:29:07,120
You've caused our feelings to become deeper.

292
00:29:12,150 --> 00:29:15,280
I initially meant to grab the arsenic.

293
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:17,160
You wouldn't!

294
00:29:24,250 --> 00:29:26,900
But as far as your thoughts,

295
00:29:28,030 --> 00:29:31,190
