296
00:29:37,990 --> 00:29:40,760
As for how you would treat me,

297
00:29:42,600 --> 00:29:44,480
I don't know.

298
00:29:45,850 --> 00:29:49,200
As for whether your words are true or not,

299
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:52,690
I also don't know.

300
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:07,730
Maybe I should dig out your heart,

301
00:30:09,030 --> 00:30:12,600
