302
00:30:23,670 --> 00:30:27,990
Excuse me, Miss! Is there an Uncle Yang who lives here?

303
00:30:27,990 --> 00:30:29,860
He's my husband.

304
00:30:29,860 --> 00:30:33,380
A few days after our recent wedding, he became severely ill.

305
00:30:33,380 --> 00:30:37,930
He went to see doctors all over the city but it was no use.

306
00:30:39,560 --> 00:30:43,520
The deceased's family lives in Bishui City, the person is Uncle Yang.

307
00:30:44,120 --> 00:30:47,770
I found out that the deceased had a silver needle on the top of his head.

308
00:30:47,770 --> 00:30:50,090
The Healer used this to manipulate and control corpses as puppets.

309
00:30:50,090 --> 00:30:52,120
However, the Healer is dead.

310
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:56,180
Well, have you heard of the Healer before?

311
00:30:56,950 --> 00:31:00,680
The Healer? No.

312
00:31:01,870 --> 00:31:05,630
When Yang passed away, I couldn't afford his burial or coffin.

313
00:31:05,630 --> 00:31:07,420
An unfamiliar but extremely charitable person,

314
00:31:07,420 --> 00:31:10,930
