315
00:31:10,930 --> 00:31:16,050
- If that's the case, did you see Uncle Yang being buried for yourself? 
 - Yes.

316
00:31:16,050 --> 00:31:19,590
So as for this extremely charitable person, did you ask for his name?

317
00:31:21,320 --> 00:31:24,980
He said his surname was Zhong.

318
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:56,470
Do you really hate me that much?

319
00:32:02,690 --> 00:32:04,520
No.

320
00:32:05,120 --> 00:32:09,970
It's because I must get the antidote for the dandelion poison.

321
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:14,110
For Xiao Bai?

322
00:32:15,550 --> 00:32:17,910
For myself.

323
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:22,430
The people at Fengming Mountain Manor poisoned me.

324
00:32:22,430 --> 00:32:24,950
